name: Mosaic Lite - Tailwind CSS Admin Dashboard Template
description:
Mosaic Lite is a responsive dashboard template built on top of TailwindCSS. It comes with several pre-coded charts and widgets, and it's a great starting for anyone who wants to create a user interface for SaaS products, administrator dashboards, modern web apps, and more.
